Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA'S IDENTITY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] So you're saying\None of those people is Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda, voice disguised]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a lot of evidence\Nto prove it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who died was Mr. H.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If Higuchi can kill\Nby looking at someone's face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,like the second Kira was able to,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Matsuda will die.\N-[Matsuda gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,SPECIAL REPORT ON KIRA\NTHE CONCLUSION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,TODAY'S SHOW WILL REVEAL\NTHE TRUE IDENTITY OF KIRA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming] Don't screw with me.\NWhy the hell can't you remember
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the names of the people you hire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I have two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[engine revs]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires squeal]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wedy]\NI see Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only carrying a single bag.\NI'm in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kyosuke Higuchi] I'll kill him.\NI'll kill him no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up until I have everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,FRENZY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[voice-over] Cosme Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A devilish charm.\NAn angel's glitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa's new line of lipstick\Njust for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, the commercial's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Next thing you know,\NI'm in a hotel room,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,drinking with all eight of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC laughs]\NWell, that's rather amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] But if I give you\Nany more details,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid the people who were there\Nthat night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,would realize\Nwhich one of them is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think I'd better leave it at that\Nfor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] Of course.\NPlease take your time to tell us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,all the details of your ordeal\Nto find Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Light, please put Higuchi's car\Non audio channel one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and Sakura TV on channel two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light Yagami] As expected,\NHiguchi is watching every minute of this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:02:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,from his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] And so, according to you,\Nit was actually at that party
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that you met Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Yes.\NBut of course at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no way of knowing\Nhe was actually Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] So, that means he saw your face.\NThis is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's amazingly courageous of you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to step forward and appear\Non this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you sure you're okay with it?\N-[Matsuda] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After I started investigating him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out there are two things\NKira has to have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There are rumors on TV and the internet\Nas to what those two things might be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi]\NA name and a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] But Kira only knows\None of those two things about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so that means I should be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] So he's saying he feels\Nsafe enough to step forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,just because I don't know\Nhis real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, does that mean
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing left that can connect me\Nto his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's already destroyed his file\Nat Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I'm wasting my time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I think? About what, may I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one else in that car, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for someone to be hiding\Nwithout us knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't using his cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be a hidden radio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No. There's aren't any radios\Nor other devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the bugs, cameras, and tracking\Nbeacons that Wedy placed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt that she did\Na thorough job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'll get\Nto Yoshida Productions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,only to find his file isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he talking to himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why ask my opinion? I don't see how\NI'm supposed to know something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If this guy was smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he would destroy everything\Nthat connects him with his real name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,before he appeared on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] And don't you think\Nit's a little too reckless
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for Yoshida Productions to just let me\Ninto their offices unsupervised?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, maybe not. If there was a robbery
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd figure out right away who did it,\Nsince I know where the key is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't sounding very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll still go there,\Ndon't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he does have a file at Yoshida,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be just another alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. I wouldn't put it past this guy\Nto do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder he's confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] It must be Light and Misa's plan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to have Higuchi go\Nto Yoshida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be true,\Nbut if he knows that you are Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,he's going to announce your name\Nin public.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an inescapable fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC]\NAll right, there's only one hour left
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,until the big announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your only option is to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If the name on his file is false\Nthat will be unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it isn't,\Nyou can kill him discretely
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I already know that much\Nmyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But just to be on the safe side,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I should kill the people\NI contacted at Yoshida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes the president, Misa,\Nand that manager of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way, he's going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's talking about doing that\Nafter he's killed Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be no point in killing\Nthe rest of you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,until he's gotten rid of\Nthe main threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] Don't be reckless.\NHe's the only one you have to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If the people you called\Nend up dying too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the phone records will implicate you\Nin their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Rem, I didn't think\Nyou were so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll make them all erase\Ntheir call histories before they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But the telephone company\Nwill still have a record of the calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he can\Njust be talking to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But, who's Rem? Who is he talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's talking to someone right now,\Nit could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] I should just go ahead and ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How about giving up ownership\Nof the notebook and returning it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'd end up being ruined\Nif I did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I forgot the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,this guy says he has concrete evidence\Nto back him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If he points out Yotsuba's recent growth\Non the air
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,no one would ever doubt his claims.\NThey'd believe whatever he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That means whoever he says is Kira\Nwill be marked as Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he didn't have proof\Nand I got rid of the evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,by returning the notebook,\Nmy life would be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't get promoted, I wouldn't even\Nbe able to stay with Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] Of course, Sakura TV has\Nbroadcast this show
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,under the premise that right now,\Nas we speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira is watching this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] In that case,\NI'll take this chance to call out to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira, please turn yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] The guy is acting like\Na complete idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, he was smart enough to fake his own\Ndeath to avoid being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-I have to kill him as soon as possible.\N-[tires squeal]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-[engine shuts off]\N-[car door opens, shuts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's arrived at Yoshida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The show is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps approach]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[door unlocks]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To the left as I come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The desk at the very back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The very bottom drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,MANAGER\NTAICHIRO YAMASHITA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Now, Kira, how do you kill?\NShow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in position\Nand ready to take him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-We'll move on your command.\N-[L] Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,TAICHIRO YAMASHITA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans with pleasure]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not doing it. He just made\Na note of his name before leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he's not going to kill him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, do you want us\Nto apprehend him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative. We still don't know\Nhow he kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he's planning to do something\Nonce he's back in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Let's see camera one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-[beeping]\N-[clicking]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird, you'd think he'd be desperate\Nto kill Matsuda this very second
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If all he needed was the name,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,then he should have taken\Nthe personnel file with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But he just put it back in its drawer\Nafter taking the note.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi]\NThirty-six, 37...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty-eight, 39...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Kira is a cold-blooded murderer.\NI can't forgive him for what he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, he didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What's he talking about?\NHe said he didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Did he already try and kill Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Was writing his name down\Nall he had to do, or was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we just continue watching\Nwhat he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he can cause a death\Nby just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I don't understand what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't figure out how\Nhe kills people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if we restrain him now\Nand try to get him to confess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] Only fifty minutes to go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-until the big Kira announcement!\N-Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone dialing]\N-[Light] He's making a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably Misa again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone rings]\N-[Misa] Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go back to company HQ\Nthere should be surveillance videos
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,from when he snuck in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had the Shinigami eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Half of my remaining lifespan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot. But if he makes\Nthat announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,my life is as good as over anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to have a life\Nthat's short and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem, let's make the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[high pitched ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The deal? Who is this Rem person\Nhe keeps talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it really be that Kira's power comes\Nfrom another world or some being?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want to think\Nthat's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is this Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, we need\Nto keep watching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll learn nothing if we take him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We may still be able to find out\Nhow he kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] With these eyes\NI'm invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I have more than enough options now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[engines rev]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro Yagami] We're heading after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[siren wails]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[police] You in the red car,\Npull over to the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Higuchi grunts]\N-[police] Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wedy] This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi's been pulled over by\Na traffic cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wedy] I'm going to have to pass him\Nand leave the pursuit to Aiber's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You were speeding. License, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch all screens to Higuchi's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Let's see.\NWhere did I put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[high pitched ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] This will take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,YUKITO SHIRABA, ACCIDENT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[engine revs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[police] Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi ditched the cop.\NHe's driving away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[siren blares]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is traffic control squad.\N[cries out]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires squeal]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That motorcycle cop just rear-ended\Nthat truck. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead?\NBy accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] All he did was put his hand\Nin his bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he have done something\Nin that moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,how was he able to obtain\Nthe name of the cop who stopped him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he only need a face,\Nlike the second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem. A deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] No, if he had the power to kill\Nby looking at someone's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,he would have already killed\NMatsuda by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NUnless...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! It's too dangerous\Nto allow further action by Higuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I believe he has the same powers\Nas the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He is able to kill\Njust by looking at someone's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep this in mind\Nwhen you move in to arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[cars approaching]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Watari, connect me\Nto the director of the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] This is L. We are now aware of\NKira's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's currently heading\Nfrom Hibiya to Shibuya
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,along Highway Route One,\Nin a red sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Our group will be handling the arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime,\Nplease instruct all officers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to refrain from approaching his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Dad. During the next commercial\Ntake measure seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Demegawa,\Nduring the next commercial break,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,swap Matsuda and the MC\Nwith mannequins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make it seem as if the broadcast\Nis continuing as normal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,using the voices we've already prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave the cameras running\Nand everyone evacuate the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, Light.\NWhat say we go join the fun as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to do this, Misa,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have to make sure\Nyou're restrained for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling] What? But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[helicopter propeller thrums]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I didn't realize you could pilot\Na helicopter. That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Well, you can figure it out\Nwith intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Higuchi isn't going to Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's headed the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Based on his route, I'd guess\Nhe's coming to the Yotsuba main office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC]\NYou've been outstandingly brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] No. I'm just doing\Nwhat anyone would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] If I go to the main office
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and find the surveillance video\Nwith him on it, I can kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in, Wedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you removed absolutely everything\Nrelating to Matsuda
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Yotsuba headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wedy] Yeah.\NWhy, is he headed there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That should give me more than enough time\Nto go ahead and meet up with Mr. Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to set up the ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-[tires squeal]\N-[car door opens, shuts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] What the hell, I can't find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the right tape.\NSomeone must have erased it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he come back\Nand erase them himself somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Or has someone from the group betrayed me\Nand started working with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, doing that would not\Nabsolve them of their crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares. I'm out of time.\NI've got to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[engine starts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] We're quickly approaching\Nthe time for the announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] I feel ready for this.\NI really want you to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] Yes, I understand. But let's cut to\Na quick commercial break first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to Sakura TV\Nand kill him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[engine revs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, Higuchi has left Yoshiba.\NHe's on his way to Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be there in less than 15 minutes.\NAre you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] I don't need my son asking\Nif I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] Is there anything more you'd like\Nto add before the announcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] I want everyone to think hard\Nabout Kira after he's caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,People have to realize\Nthat Kira is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You ready, Mr. Yagami?\NIt's almost time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Wedy] Here.\N-Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiber hates using guns.\NRight now, I'm the only one armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this.\NI'm no longer a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese law forbids civilians\Nfrom having guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you shouldn't be\Nusing one either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're as stubborn as always, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,SAKURA TV
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]\NI made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just in case the announcement\Nis true and Kira decides to retaliate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. At least it makes my job easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] We've arrived at Sakura TV.\NWe're moving into position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go, Aiber.\N-Okay, Mogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] Right now we are being flooded\Nwith phone calls and faxes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,showing support for\Nyour courage and strength
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and demanding that Kira's identity\Nbe revealed right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the studio is deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I've got to be careful of\Nwhere the cameras are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't let myself be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] ...beyond our control,\Nwe will now end this broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummies. This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Yagami] Higuchi, hold it right there.\N-[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wedy] Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd give up\Nif I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you must be making\Nsome kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only here to meet with Mr. Demegawa\Nand discuss something with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] They're wearing tinted helmets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be taking precautions\Nagainst Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with the Yotsuba Group,\Nfrom the Development Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you my business card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aiber] No, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:17:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wedy] Aiber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!\NI didn't want to use one of these, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,L, Higuchi has a gun on him.\NThe chief has been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi is escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] I'm all right. Sorry, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If we pursue him,\Nwe can still catch him. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. He's escaped from Sakura TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[engine revs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires squeal]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This leaves us no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to move in\Nand apprehend him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-[L] Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should hold on to this\Nfor self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kira we're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.\NFirearms aren't allowed in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm sure your father\Nwould say the exact same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[honking]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's driving like a maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't lose sight of him.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-[grunts]\N-[tires squeal]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[helicopter propeller thrums]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi]\NWhat the hell was all that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It had to be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[TV announcer]\NWe now end our current broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and return you to regular programming.\NThe evening news is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] The program is over!\NIt didn't end just because I showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[cries out] What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[sirens wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I thought, it was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Police cars with tinted windows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So all that stuff about\Nthe police not going after Kira was a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They were preparing for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari]\NWhat's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we told the police\Nnot to get involved with the arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] The only one\Nwho would do this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you must be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires squeal loudly]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!\NStay back or I'll shoot, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[cries out]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED